snippet.title: Space Blaster (Lines) Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Download here: http://www.indiedb.com/games/space-blaster-lines

A experimental horror game about a vengeful AI trapped inside an unfinished space ship game. Lines seeks to imprison all who attempt to the play the game.
